#IPhone Scripts

A set of tools to do various stuff to make your life with Iphone easier


#Audio to ALAC

-Recursively convert whole directories of audio files and songs to Apple's ALAC format
-Can convert FLAC or any other audio format
-Retains directory structure in target location
-Uses FFMPEG

Requirements:
-A working ffmpeg installation
-Python >= 3.5 (also see python requirements file)

Examples:

python3 audio_to_alac.py  --base /path/to/music/dir --target /tmp/outputaudio --format flac --pool-size 15 
python3 audio_to_alac.py -h
